feiji (飞机) is a bot that helps you learn Chinese!
feiji listens to a handful of !commands, and responds with answers.

For example:

21:12 <@yacin> !pinyin 我在家吃饭
21:12 < feiji> yacin, (wǒ); (zài); (gū, jiā, jià, jia, jie); (chī, qī); (fàn)
21:12 <@yacin> !translate 你好吗
21:12 < feiji> yacin, 你好吗 (你好嗎): /How are you?/Are you well?/
21:12 <@yacin> !numstrokes 我爸爸
21:12 < feiji> yacin, 7, 8, 8
22:48 < yacin> !strokes 律
22:48 < feiji> yacin, http://images.nciku.com/stroke_order/25737.swf

!translate isn't perfect yet:

21:13 <@yacin> !translate 我妈妈
21:13 < feiji> yacin,
21:13 <@yacin> fails
21:13 <@yacin> but
21:13 <@yacin> !translate 我
21:13 < feiji> yacin, 我 (我): /I/me/my/
21:13 <@yacin> !translate 妈妈
21:13 < feiji> yacin, 妈妈 (媽媽): /mama/mommy/mother/CL:個|个[ge4],位[wei4]/
21:13 <@yacin> works fine

For bug reports and feature requests: https://github.com/ynadji/nciku/issues
